[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0127","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0127.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0466","title":"NetBSD SVR4 /dev/wabi 设备文件本地任意文件读写漏洞","description":"NetBSD 1.3.3 及之前版本的 SVR4 兼容层中 /dev/wabi 设备文件主设备编号配置错误，i386 平台错误使用主编号 3（实际应为 2），导致设备文件指向错误的磁盘设备。本地攻击者可利用此缺陷读取或写入磁盘关联的任意文件，造成敏感信息泄露及系统权限提升。利用该漏洞需具备本地系统访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0466"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-04-21","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 NetBSD 1.4 及以上版本（NetBSD-current 19990420 之后已修复），或应用官方补丁 19990419-SVR4_MAKEDEV 后重新运行 SVR4_MAKEDEV 脚本重建 /dev/wabi 设备。临时缓解措施：以 root 执行 rm -f /emul/svr4/dev/wabi && mknod /emul/svr4/dev/wabi c 2 2 && chmod 666 /emul/svr4/dev/wabi，将设备主编号从 3 修正为 2。如不需要 SVR4 兼容，建议移除 /emul/svr4 模拟层。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0466"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0127.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0178","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0178.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0607","title":"QuikStore quikstore.cgi 敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"QuikStore 购物车系统的 quikstore.cgi 脚本将敏感配置文件 quikstore.cfg 存储在 Web 文档根目录下且未设置充分的访问控制措施，导致远程攻击者可直接通过 HTTP 访问该文件，获取管理员明文密码并进而获得系统管理权限。该漏洞影响 QuikStore 购物车应用，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0607"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.570","remediation":"立即将 quikstore.cfg 移出 Web 根目录（如移至 /etc/quikstore/），并通过 Web 服务器配置（如 Apache 的 <FilesMatch> 或 .htaccess）禁止公开访问 .cfg 文件；设置文件权限为 600，仅允许 Web 服务器运行用户读取；由于 QuikStore 已停止维护，强烈建议迁移至仍受支持的现代购物车系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0607.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0607","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0607.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0607.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0607.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/q/quickstore.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0607.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1983/info.html","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ba5d6d065e4a7a2829bd0ee4eca4f1c8ca12a28d/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0178.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0178.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0178.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0174","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0174.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0604","title":"Selena Sol WebStore 1.0 信息泄露漏洞","description":"WebStore 1.0 购物车 CGI 程序 web_store.cgi 存在配置不当漏洞，由于该 CGI 脚本未正确限制文件访问权限，远程攻击者可通过直接构造特制 HTTP 请求访问服务器上的敏感文件，导致私密信息（如配置文件、数据库凭证等）被非授权泄露。该漏洞影响 Selena Sol WebStore 1.0 版本，攻击无需认证，利用难度低，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0604"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.217","remediation":"立即停用 WebStore 1.0，迁移至支持数据库后端存储（而非文件存储）的现代购物车系统（如 Magento、WooCommerce）；如无法立即替换，须将 web_store.cgi 生成的订单数据文件移出 Web 文档根目录（如移至 /var/lib/webstore/），设置目录权限为 700、文件权限为 600，并通过 Web 服务器配置拒绝外部直接访问数据文件路径，同时在搜索引擎中请求移除已索引的敏感信息缓存。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0604.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0604","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0604.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0604.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0604.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0604.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88033/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000611.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0174.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0166","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0166.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0491","title":"GNU Bash 命令提示符解析本地代码执行漏洞","description":"GNU Bash 提示符解析功能存在代码注入漏洞（CWE-94）。Bash 在处理 PS1 环境变量中的转义序列时，会执行路径名中嵌入的命令。本地攻击者可通过创建一个包含恶意命令名称的特制目录，当其他用户（如 root）进入该目录时，Bash 在渲染提示符过程中自动解析并执行该目录名中的代码，从而实现本地权限提升。此漏洞影响 Bash 1.14 至 4.2 等多个版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0491"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:30.617","remediation":"升级 GNU bash 至 2.0 及以上版本（1999 年后发布的所有版本已内置修复）。受影响系统多为老旧 Linux 发行版，可通过包管理器更新：Red Hat 类系统运行 `rpm -Uvh bash-2.0-1.i386.rpm`，Debian 类运行 `apt-get install --only-upgrade bash`。无法升级的临时缓解措施：在 `PS1` 环境变量中避免使用 `\\w`（完整路径）和 `\\W`（当前目录名）转义序列，改用固定提示符，减少受陷用户在共享目录触发命令注入的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/119","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Pine.LNX.4.10.9904202114070.6623-100000%40smooth.Operator.org","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19095"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0166.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0243","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0243.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0684","title":"HP HP-UX Sendmail 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统上运行的 Sendmail 8.8.6 存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的邮件请求或恶意数据包，导致 Sendmail 进程崩溃或资源耗尽，从而使邮件服务不可用。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 系统上的 Sendmail 8.8.6 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程触发，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0684"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.533","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.9.0 及以上版本，该版本修复了 8.8.6 中的拒绝服务问题。若运行 HP-UX 11i 及更早版本，建议迁移至受支持的 HP-UX 版本或替代 MTA（如 Postfix）。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上限制入站 SMTP 连接源 IP，并监控 MTA 日志中的异常连接行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0684","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0684.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0684","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0684.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0684.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mrpx-qq9r-w54g/GHSA-mrpx-qq9r-w54g.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0684.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88042/info.html","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/hpux_PHNE_17190.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0243.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1020","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1020.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1244","title":"IPFilter 本地任意文件修改漏洞","description":"IPFilter 3.2.3至3.2.10版本中存在文件权限缺陷漏洞，本地攻击者可通过在IPFilter保存输出文件时发起符号链接攻击，利用程序对临时文件处理不当的缺陷，以IPFilter进程权限修改系统任意文件，导致权限提升或系统文件被篡改。该漏洞要求攻击者具有本地系统访问权限，CVSS评分7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1244"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-04-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:01.540","remediation":"立即升级至 IPFilter 3.2.11 或更高版本，该版本已修复保存输出文件时未正确处理符号链接的问题。如无法升级，应确保 IPFilter 运行在专用低权限账户下，避免以 root 运行；同时配置输出目录仅允许 IPFilter 进程本身写入，并定期检查输出文件路径是否被恶意符号链接劫持。此外，使用 nosuid、noexec 挂载选项的临时文件系统存放 IPFilter 输出文件也可作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13303","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2087","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1244.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1244","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1244.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1244.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4rc3-c847-cjgp/GHSA-4rc3-c847-cjgp.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87832/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1244.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000609.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--87d96785-0cbc-433d-a944-0025d58a8f33.json","https://github.com/dong-xs/Vul-PAG/blob/7eb3b32094a5270cfd8495366e0e4a7df5a874ce/aspect_prediction/org_pred_diff.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1020.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0123","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0123.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0446","title":"NetBSD NetBSD VFS 符号链接拒绝服务漏洞","description":"NetBSD 1.3.3 及之前版本的 VFS（虚拟文件系统）存在符号链接处理缺陷，本地攻击者可通过 ln 命令创建异常符号链接触发该漏洞，导致系统拒绝服务。由于 VFS 在处理畸形符号链接时未能正确验证其结构，恶意用户可构造特殊链接使内核进入异常状态，造成系统崩溃或服务不可用。该漏洞影响 NetBSD 1.3.3 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，利用需本地用户权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0446"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:24.840","remediation":"升级至 NetBSD 1.4 或更高版本，该版本已修复 VFS 中对异常符号链接处理的缺陷。如无法立即升级，可限制非信任用户的本地登录权限，或通过内核安全模块禁止特殊符号链接创建作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/7051"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0123.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0121","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0121.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0444","title":"Microsoft Windows ARP 报文拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95/98/NT 3.51/NT 4.0/2000 的 ARP 协议处理存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送恶意 ARP 数据包，触发每个数据包弹出消息框或快速填满系统日志，导致系统资源耗尽，最终造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响多个 Windows 版本，攻击者无需认证即可远程触发，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0444"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:24.593","remediation":"这些旧版 Windows 均已停止支持，官方不再提供安全更新。建议立即升级到仍在支持周期内的 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 版本。临时缓解措施：在网络边界防火墙或交换机上启用 ARP 检测和速率限制功能，部署 ARP 欺骗检测工具（如 XArp），并限制局域网内不可信设备的接入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92394891221029&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0121.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1040","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1040.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1323","title":"Symantec Norton AntiVirus NAVIEG及NAVMSE 管理员密码明文存储漏洞","description":"Norton AntiVirus for Internet Email Gateways (NAVIEG) 1.0.1.7及之前版本与Norton AntiVirus for MS Exchange (NAVMSE) 1.5及之前版本存在敏感信息明文存储漏洞。管理员密码以明文形式存储于NAVIEG的navieg.ini配置文件中以及NAVMSE的ModifyPassword注册表项中。本地攻击者可通过读取上述文件或注册表项获取管理员密码，进而获得系统管理权限。该漏洞影响范围较广，利用条件低，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1323"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-04-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:11.737","remediation":"立即升级 NAVIEG 至 1.0.1.8 或更高版本，升级 NAVMSE 至 1.6 或更高版本。如无法升级，手动设置 navieg.ini 文件 NTFS 权限为仅管理员可读，并通过注册表编辑器将 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Symantec\\NAVMSE\\ModifyPassword 项的权限限制为仅管理员可访问，防止非授权用户读取明文密码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92370067416739&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1323.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1323","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1323.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1323.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hwj6-4xgp-2fx7/GHSA-hwj6-4xgp-2fx7.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84469/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1323.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8358776d7db47304e3a87c0f78eff81411ac0e47/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1040.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0800","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0800.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0801","title":"BMC Patrol 帧欺骗访问控制绕过漏洞","description":"BMC Patrol 存在权限许可与访问控制漏洞。远程攻击者可通过伪造网络帧（frame spoofing）的方式欺骗 Patrol Agent，绕过多层身份认证机制，未经授权获取对目标系统的管理访问权限。该漏洞影响 BMC Patrol 产品，攻击者只需网络可达即可发起攻击，无需身份认证或用户交互，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0801"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-04-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.163","remediation":"该漏洞源于 BMC Patrol 代理在接收网络帧时未验证来源身份，导致远程攻击者可伪造控制台帧直接操控代理（CVSS 10.0，可完全接管主机）。建议立即将 BMC Patrol 升级至 3.5 及以上版本（启用代理身份认证功能，配置 PatrolAgentAuth 参数为 REQUIRED），同时在防火墙限制仅允许 Patrol 管理控制台 IP 访问代理端口 3181/TCP。如环境无法升级，可部署 iptables 规则 `iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --dport 3181 -s <控制台IP> -j ACCEPT; iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --dport 3181 -j DROP` 限制来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/2075.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13204"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0800.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0137","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0137.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0471","title":"Winroute 远程代理服务器未授权访问漏洞","description":"远程代理服务器 Winroute 存在未授权访问漏洞，远程攻击者无需任何身份认证即可通过点击\"取消\"按钮重新配置代理服务器参数，导致代理服务配置被恶意篡改，影响网络代理功能的正常使用。该漏洞影响 Winroute 代理服务软件，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0471"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:28.113","remediation":"Winroute 已于 2000 年被 Check Point 收购并停止维护，无官方安全更新可用。建议迁移至 Check Point 当前支持的防火墙产品（如 Quantum Security Gateway）或同等替代方案。临时缓解措施：在防火墙或主机层面限制对 Winroute 代理管理端口（默认 3128）的访问，仅允许受信任 IP 地址连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0471"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0137.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0132","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0132.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0468","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.0 远程任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 的 Microsoft Scriptlet 组件存在任意文件读取漏洞，远程攻击者可诱导用户访问恶意网页，通过该组件读取客户端文件系统中的任意文件内容，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 5.0 版本，危害等级高（CVSS 8.2），攻击者只需诱使用户浏览特制网页即可利用，无需额外权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0468"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:27.557","remediation":"升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.01 及以上版本，该漏洞已在 IE 5.01 中修复。如在旧版 Windows 系统上无法升级，可禁用 Scriptlet 组件（通过注册表禁用 scrobj.dll 注册：`regsvr32 /u scrobj.dll`）作为临时缓解措施。当前建议彻底弃用 IE，改用 Edge/Chrome 等现代浏览器。建议立即安装 Internet Explorer 5.01 安全更新 (MS99-007)，或通过 Windows Update 获取修补程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-012"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0132.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0019","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0019.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0287","title":"WebCom datakommunikation Guestbook rguest.exe 任意文件访问漏洞","description":"WebCom datakommunikation Guestbook 0.1 的 rguest.exe CGI 程序存在任意文件访问漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向该 CGI 程序发送特制请求，利用路径遍历技术读取 Web 服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Guestbook 0.1 版本，攻击条件低、利用简单，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0287"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.593","remediation":"立即从 Web 服务器 CGI 目录中删除或重命名 rguest.exe 和 wguest.exe 文件，彻底禁用该留言本组件。在 IIS 中可通过「应用程序配置」移除该脚本映射，或在文件系统层面撤销 IUSR_MACHINENAME 账户对 CGI 目录的执行权限。建议替换为其他仍在维护的开源留言本或使用无文件写入的第三方评论服务（如 Disqus）以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92368828704896&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0287.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0287","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0287.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0287.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0287.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0287.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0019.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0134","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0134.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0470","title":"Novell NetWare Remote.NLM 弱加密漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare 4.1 及 4.11 版本的 Remote.NLM 远程管理模块对用户密码采用弱加密算法，攻击者可在未经认证的情况下通过网络嗅探截获加密后的密码数据，并利用加密算法的弱点在本地快速解密还原出明文密码。该漏洞可导致攻击者获取系统合法用户凭据，进而未授权访问受影响的 Novell NetWare 服务器。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0470"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1999-04-09","updated":"2026-07-14","remediation":"升级到 Novell NetWare 5.0 及以上版本，或安装最新的 Support Pack（SP6+）。如无法升级，建议卸载或禁用 Remote.NLM 模块（在控制台输入 UNLOAD REMOTE），改用安全的 SSH 或 VPN 方式进行远程管理，并在路由器/防火墙上限制对 1675/TCP 端口的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/482","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19364"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0134.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1007","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1007.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1196","title":"Hummingbird Exceed 5.0 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Hummingbird Exceed 5.0（一款运行于 Windows 平台的 X Window 服务器软件）存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统的 6000 端口发送特制的畸形数据包，触发服务进程崩溃或无法正常响应，导致系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Hummingbird Exceed X version 5，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1196"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-04-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:55.377","remediation":"升级至 Hummingbird Exceed 6.0.1、6.0.2 或 6.1 及以上版本，该漏洞在后续版本中已修复。由于 Exceed 5.0 已停止维护，若仍在使用建议迁移至现代 X 服务器替代方案。临时缓解措施：在网络防火墙上封禁 TCP 端口 6000，限制仅受信任的 IP 地址可访问 X11 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13451","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/158","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1196.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1196","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1196.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1196.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5783344e7c4adc3f449b78e346f760d75b095a9c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g5v2-hv74-hhp6/GHSA-g5v2-hv74-hhp6.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/R/random_crap_DoS.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1196.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000601.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--42baa4ee-b6bc-4f5a-9835-e12a18e09f85.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1007.toml"}]